<br>
You are a team player... Either support the team or find another team to play on.  For you not to support your current team simply means you are not on the right team.<br>
<br>
Just like a cleric who refused to participate in a CHeal chain, a Tank who wants to inappropiately hold aggro when another tank is the MT etc...<br>
<br>
I would boot the person from the raid, no questions asked.<br>
