<br>
Yeah, if I'm on a raid hosted by another guild, or its a mob I'm unfamiliar with, I'll probably do whatever is asked of me. Even then I'd probably toss in a few nukes if there are plenty of rods.<br>
<br>
But raid leaders dont go telling each and every class what they should be doing, beyond maybe setting up CH timing. I probably know how to play a mage better than they do. If I'm on the raid, I hope its because they know I know what I'm doing. If you're going to place those restrictions on me, I'd probably gate. Sure, maybe then I'm not a team player and shouldnt be on the raid. I guess I agree with that, cuz I'm gating. If you need rods that bad, you could at least show me some respect.<br>
<br>
